headline: Cracker Barrel Old Country Store (CBRL) Q3 Earnings Top Estimates
summary: Cracker Barrel (CBRL) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 241.18% and 0.66%, respectively, for the quarter ended April 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
